## Summary

**Core Architecture (M1 + M2):**
- ✅ Typed errors (src/errors.ts) - all three error classes implemented
- ✅ scan() return type - all backends return {path, line, content}[]
- ✅ list() path normalization - all backends return paths with '/' prefix
- ✅ OPFS walkDir error handling - properly logs and throws
- ✅ Test suite - 16 test files (1753 lines total)
- ✅ JSDoc documentation - complete on all public APIs
- ✅ README examples and performance table - comprehensive
- ✅ ShellFS export - available in index.ts
- ✅ MemoryStorage backend - fully implemented
- ✅ File metadata (size/mtime) - NodeFsBackend implements stat()
- ✅ Batch operations - batchGet/batchSet in all backends
- ✅ Symlink support - NodeFsBackend with cycle detection

**Beyond Design Scope:**
- LocalStorageBackend, SQLiteBackend, TfIdfEmbedBackend implemented
- shell-tools.ts with POSIX-like command wrappers

**Minor Gaps (5%):**
1. README.md line 147: Custom storage example needs scan() signature update
2. Additional backends not documented in milestone designs
3. ShellFS implementation details not in M2 design doc

The codebase significantly exceeds the original M1/M2 specifications with additional backends and tooling.

